-----------------Description--------------- 
1. SQL Injection. 

Vulnerable script: countdown.php 

Parameter 'years' is not properly sanitized before being used in SQL 
query. This can be used to make SQL queries by injecting arbitrary SQL 
code. 

Condition: magic_quotes_gpc = off 

